com.label305.stan.geofencing

Class GeofenceHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.label305.stan.geofencing.GeofenceHelper

  • public class GeofenceHelper
extends Object
    This is a helper class to work with Geofences.

    Usage:
  • Implement the ReceiveTransitionsIntentService class.
  • Create a new instance of this GeofenceHelper class, providing your calling Activity and your ReceiveTransitionsIntentService class.
  • Optionally set a GeofenceHelper.GeofenceListener
  • Call the GeofenceHelper#handleOnResume(android.app.Activity), GeofenceHelper#handleOnPause(android.app.Activity) and GeofenceHelper#handleActivityResult(int, int, android.content.Intent) from the appropriate places.

    • NOTE: If a call to add / remove geofences is placed, and the user exits (pauses) the calling Activity, no guarantees about removing or adding geolocations can be made. Block UI manipulation until GeofenceHelper.GeofenceListener.onGeofencesAdded(), GeofenceHelper.GeofenceListener.onGeofencesRemoved() or GeofenceHelper.GeofenceListener.onGeofenceError(android.content.Intent) is called.
